UniChem buys two pharmacies for 716 , 000 stg . British drug wholesaler and retailer UniChem Plc said on Wednesday it bought two pharmacies in England for about 716 , 000 stg in stock . UniChem said it would issue 126 , 259 UniChem ordinary shares worth 2 . 5543 stg each to buy I . Burt in Stansted and ADJ & JC Holden Ltd in Haltwhistle . The firm said the acquisition , together with consolidation of outlets in other areas , meant that its Moss Chemists division traded from 459 outlets in England , Scotland and Wales . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7717 
